cisc275.group3.utility

Interface ConstructFish


  • public interface ConstructFish
    Interface to simplify the construction of fish objects. This code used to be within SceneBay.java, but was transitioned into an interface to reduce code size and increase extensibility.
    Author:
    Ryan, Scott
